ipv4 route v1 2.2.2.1 255.255.255.255 1.1.2.2
ipv6 route v1 4321::1 ffff:ffff:ffff:ffff:ffff:ffff:ffff:ffff 1234:2::2
ipv4 route v1 2.2.2.2 255.255.255.255 1.1.2.2
